actions-for-nautilus (1.7.0) stable; urgency=medium
  * Implement show_if_true to run a command to establish
    applicability of an action to a certain selection.
  * Implement action disabling to allow existence in the config but
    non-display in the Gnome Files context menu.
  * Better highlighting of the save button when config changes have 
    been detected.

